{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# CAMS-742 Trustee Name Management Metrics\n\nSuccess metrics for CAMS-742: last-name sort adoption and post-launch name correction patterns.\n\n**Measurements:**\n- **Sort adoption** — percentage of trustee list page loads where the user clicked the sort button\n- **Name edits** — trustee name changes since launch, segmented by migrated vs non-migrated trustees"
      },
      "name": "header"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "TimeRange",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimeRange",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 2592000000
            },
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                {
                  "durationMs": 86400000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 172800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 604800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 1209600000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 2419200000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 2592000000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 5184000000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 7776000000
                }
              ]
            },
            "label": "Time Range",
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            }
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "---\n## Sort-by-Last-Name Adoption\nPercentage of sessions where the user sorted the trustee list at least once. Spam clicks are deduplicated per session so one user clicking sort many times counts as a single sorted session."
      },
      "name": "sort-adoption-header"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "let sessions_with_load = customEvents\n    | where timestamp {TimeRange}\n    | where name == \"Trustee List Loaded\"\n    | distinct session_Id;\nlet sessions_with_sort = customEvents\n    | where timestamp {TimeRange}\n    | where name == \"Trustee List Sort Changed\"\n    | extend DidSort = true\n    | distinct session_Id, DidSort;\nsessions_with_load\n| join kind=leftouter sessions_with_sort on session_Id\n| summarize TotalSessions = count(), SortedSessions = countif(DidSort == true)\n| project SortAdoptionPct = round(100.0 * SortedSessions / TotalSessions, 1), TotalSessions, SortedSessions",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Sort Adoption Rate",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "SortAdoptionPct",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "blue"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 1,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "minimumFractionDigits": 1,
                "maximumFractionDigits": 1
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "sort-adoption-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where name == \"Trustee List Loaded\"\n| summarize TrusteeListLoads = count() by Day = startofday(timestamp)\n| order by Day asc",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Trustee List Page Loads",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "TrusteeListLoads",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "blue"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "page-loads-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where name == \"Trustee List Sort Changed\"\n| summarize SortClicks = count() by Day = startofday(timestamp)\n| order by Day asc",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Sort Button Clicks",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "SortClicks",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "blue"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "sort-clicks-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "let sessions_with_load = customEvents\n    | where timestamp {TimeRange}\n    | where name == \"Trustee List Loaded\"\n    | extend Day = startofday(timestamp)\n    | distinct session_Id, Day;\nlet sessions_with_sort = customEvents\n    | where timestamp {TimeRange}\n    | where name == \"Trustee List Sort Changed\"\n    | extend DidSort = true\n    | distinct session_Id, DidSort;\nsessions_with_load\n| join kind=leftouter sessions_with_sort on session_Id\n| summarize TotalSessions = count(), SortedSessions = countif(DidSort == true) by Day\n| project Day, SortAdoptionPct = round(100.0 * SortedSessions / TotalSessions, 1)\n| order by Day asc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Sort Adoption Over Time",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "linechart",
        "chartSettings": {
          "xAxis": "Day",
          "showDataPoints": true,
          "seriesLabelSettings": [
            {
              "seriesName": "SortAdoptionPct",
              "label": "Sort Adoption %",
              "color": "blue"
            }
          ],
          "ySettings": {
            "numberFormatSettings": {
              "unit": 1,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            },
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100
          }
        }
      },
      "name": "sort-adoption-trend"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "---\n## Name Edit Correction Patterns\nReal-time count of trustee name edits since launch, segmented by migrated vs non-migrated to surface whether migration introduced data quality issues that users are now correcting."
      },
      "name": "name-edits-header"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where name == \"Trustee Name Edited\"\n| summarize TotalNameEdits = count()",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Total Name Edits",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "TotalNameEdits",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "blue"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "name-edits-total-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where name == \"Trustee Name Edited\"\n| where tostring(customDimensions.isMigrated) == \"true\"\n| summarize MigratedEdits = count()",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Name Edits — Migrated Trustees",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "MigratedEdits",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "orange"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "name-edits-migrated-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where name == \"Trustee Name Edited\"\n| where tostring(customDimensions.isMigrated) == \"false\"\n| summarize NonMigratedEdits = count()",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Name Edits — Non-Migrated Trustees",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "NonMigratedEdits",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "green"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "name-edits-non-migrated-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where name == \"Trustee Name Edited\"\n| extend isMigrated = tostring(customDimensions.isMigrated)\n| summarize\n    MigratedEdits = countif(isMigrated == \"true\"),\n    NonMigratedEdits = countif(isMigrated == \"false\")\n    by Day = startofday(timestamp)\n| order by Day asc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Name Edits Over Time — Migrated vs Non-Migrated",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "linechart",
        "chartSettings": {
          "xAxis": "Day",
          "showDataPoints": true,
          "seriesLabelSettings": [
            {
              "seriesName": "MigratedEdits",
              "label": "Migrated Trustees",
              "color": "orange"
            },
            {
              "seriesName": "NonMigratedEdits",
              "label": "Non-Migrated Trustees",
              "color": "green"
            }
          ],
          "ySettings": {
            "numberFormatSettings": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "name": "name-edits-trend"
    }
  ],
